            i(class="fab fa-youtube fa-padding" style="font-size: 1.5em;")
  section(class="section")
      div(class="tile is-ancestor")
        div(class="tile is-vertical is-8")
          div(class="tile")
            div(class="tile is-parent is-vertical")
              article(class="tile is-child notification is-silver")
                p(class="title")
                  a(href="https://egee.io") Egee.io
                p(class="subtitle") A community for Gamers and Artists
                  div(class="content")
                    p Created as a Discord server for fans by the YouTube channel, Egee.io grew into an active community for creative people with members from all over the world.
                    p Egee.io hosts its own game servers with monthly events and organizes local get-togethers.
              article(class="tile is-child notification is-silver")
                p(class="title")
                  a(href="https://www.deviantart.com/egee-irl") DeviantArt
                p(class="subtitle") Creative &amp; Open Artwork.
                div(class="content")
                  p A place where I showcase all the art I and others have created for Egee and the Egee.io community.
                  p I share all my <i>real</i> photography on <a href="https://unsplash.com/@egeeirl">Unsplashed</a>.
            div(class="tile is-parent")
              article(class="tile is-child notification is-silver")
                p(class="title" style="margin-bottom: .5rem;")
                  a(href="https://www.youtube.com/c/Egeeirl") Egee - YouTube
                p A YouTube channel I created in 2014 where I produce the Distro Delves series, live streams, and cover various other technical subjects.
                br
                figure(class="image is-3by2")
                  a(href="")
                    img(src="./assets/img/home.jpg")
          div(class="tile is-parent")
            article(class="tile is-child notification is-silver")
              p(class="title")
                <a href="https://soundcloud.com/egeeirl/">Soundcloud</a>
              p(class="subtitle") Podcasts &amp; Music
              div(class="content")
                p I host a casual Podcast where a <a href="https://twitter.com/pdxkcm">friend</a> and I interview developers we've worked with about their stories in software development and produce music using only Free and Open Source software.
        div(class="tile")
          div(class="tile is-parent is-vertical")
            article(class="tile is-child notification is-silver")
              p(class="title")
                <a href="https://github.com/egee-irl/jumper">jumper</a>
              p(class="subtitle") A simple PhaserJS sample game.
              div(class="content")
                p An ultra basic platformer game I made for a YouTube <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=88DS3Z8nOdY">video</a> written with PhaserJS 2 to demonstrate basic game development.
                p A successor to jumper is in the <a href="https://github.com/egee-irl/the-game">works</a> as game development is a hobby of mine.
            article(class="tile is-child notification is-silver")
              p(class="title")
                a(href="https://github.com/egee-irl/gsd-cli") gsd-cli
              p(class="subtitle") A handy CLI for managing game servers.
              div(class="content")
                p A CLI written in to help make deploying and managing dedicated game servers easier. It was originally built for the Egee.io community game servers but was rewritten to be infrastructure agnostic.
                p The gsd-cli codebase is very portable and has currently been ported to <a href="https://rubygems.org/gems/gsd-cli">Ruby</a>, <a href="https://pypi.org/project/gsdcli/">Python</a>, and <a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/gsd-cli">NodeJS</a>.
